Package rubenchristoffer.hetty.filters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HTTPBasicHeadersFilter
    Sets value of 'Connection' header to 'Keep-Alive'.
    HTTPContentFilter
    Sets 'Content-Length' header to number of bytes in packet body, unless 'Transfer-Encoding' header exists.
    HTTPFormDataFilter
    HTTP filter that aids in posting forms.
    HTTPHostFilter
    Only filters request packets.
    HTTPPacketFilter
    A HTTP filter modifies HTTP packet (request or response).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HTTPBasicHeadersFilter.Mode
    Enum used for determining what headers this filter should affect.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HTTPFilterException
    Exception used when something goes wrong in a HTTPFilter.
